    <!-- Info window -->
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Title">About ClickyKeys</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Tagline">Key &amp; click counter for gamers and geeks</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Features">Features</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Feature1">• Counts every key press and mouse click you actually care about — live, as it happens.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Feature2">• Give your keys real names: Jump, Reload, Ability 1 — whatever makes sense to you.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Feature3">• Make the overlay yours: grid and panel size, colours, fonts, even gamepad buttons.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Privacy">Privacy &amp; Source Available</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_PrivacyText1">Your key presses and clicks are counted right here on your PC and never leave it — full stop. If you'd like to help ClickyKeys grow, you can opt in to anonymous usage stats: Basic (an anonymous ID, app version, distribution channel, OS version, UI language, plus two running totals — overall input count and uptime) or Full (all of that plus how features are configured and used). It stays off unless you turn it on, and you can switch it back any time in Settings → Data Collection.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_PrivacyText2">The whole source is out in the open — peek under the hood, learn from it, or send a pull request.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Credits">Credits &amp; Thanks</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_CreditsText1">ClickyKeys is a one-person hobby project, kept alive by people who simply enjoy watching the numbers climb.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_CreditsText2">Happy clicking — and thanks for being here.</sys:String>
