    <sys:String x:Key="Settings_TelemetryAssurance">ClickyKeys is not a keylogger: no option here ever records what you type, your passwords, or which keys/clicks you make. Keeping you safe matters to this project — the source code is fully available, so you don't have to take our word for it:</sys:String>
